{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":32,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_shen_bei_chang","speaker_name":"沈北昌","listener":null,"text":"此地不宜谈话，随我来。","tone":"沉声","chapter":272,"line_start":7,"line_end":7},{"speaker":"char_yu_ling_fu_ren","speaker_name":"玉玲夫人","listener":null,"text":"无论帮内发生甚么事，也该在帮内解决，邵令周这么借外人之力来对付帮中兄弟，已触犯帮规，卑劣无耻。","tone":"愤怒","chapter":272,"line_start":11,"line_end":12},{"speaker":"char_shen_bei_chang","speaker_name":"沈北昌","listener":null,"text":"但现在实非内讧的好时刻，李子通只因需借助少帅，才肯释放桂堂主和幸副堂主两人，一旦解去围城之困，这小人便会反目相向，甚至乎派人截击少帅，故须三思而行。","tone":"冷静","chapter":272,"line_start":15,"line_end":16},{"speaker":"char_luo_feng","speaker_name":"骆奉","listener":"char_kou_zhong","text":"目下唯一方法，就是立刻离城，将来才和邵令周算账。少帅认为此法如何？","tone":"认真","chapter":272,"line_start":19,"line_end":21},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":null,"text":"我也想不出更好的办法，趁现在李子通不敢为难我们，要走趁早。不如谎称你们是要助我去对付杜伏威，那李子通虽心知肚明是甚么一回事，亦可容易点下台。","tone":"陈述","chapter":272,"line_start":23,"line_end":26},{"speaker":"char_shen_bei_chang","speaker_name":"沈北昌","listener":null,"text":"就这么办！","tone":"果断","chapter":272,"line_start":29,"line_end":29}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_kou_zhong","name":"寇仲","alias":["少帅"],"identity":"竹花帮少帅，李子通的对手","faction":"竹花帮","role":"protagonist","archetype":"warrior","rank":"出神入化","one_line":"竹花帮少帅，勇猛善战的青年领袖","personality":{"traits":["勇猛","豪迈","机智","重义","果断","自信"],"speech_style":"豪爽直接","temperament":"热血豪迈"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_xu_zi_ling","type":"挚友","intensity":95,"bond_level":5,"dynamic":"生死与共的兄弟"},{"target":"char_gui_xi_liang","type":"挚友","intensity":70,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"竹花帮兄弟"},{"target":"char_shen_bei_chang","type":"合作者","intensity":60,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"竹花帮同僚"},{"target":"char_luo_feng","type":"合作者","intensity":60,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"竹花帮同僚"},{"target":"char_yu_ling_fu_ren","type":"合作者","intensity":55,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"竹花帮同僚"},{"target":"char_gui_xi_liang","type":"挚友","intensity":70,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"竹花帮兄弟"},{"target":"char_xing_rong","type":"合作者","intensity":55,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"竹花帮兄弟"},{"target":"char_li_zi_tong","type":"对手","intensity":80,"bond_level":2,"dynamic":"敌对"},{"target":"char_du_fu_wei","type":"对手","intensity":85,"bond_level":1,"dynamic":"大敌"},{"target":"char_shao_ling_zhou","type":"对手","intensity":70,"bond_level":2,"dynamic":"内部对手"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[272],"source_refs":[{"chapter":272,"line_start":3,"line_end":3,"text":"寇仲领着桂锡良和幸容，由李子通、左孝友等亲自送出总管府"}]},{"id":"char_gui_xi_liang","name":"桂锡良","alias":["桂堂主"],"identity":"竹花帮堂主","faction":"竹花帮","role":"companion","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"竹花帮堂主，寇仲的帮中兄弟","personality":{"traits":["忠义","勇敢","沉稳","务实","团结"],"speech_style":"沉稳","temperament":"稳重"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_kou_zhong","type":"挚友","intensity":70,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"竹花帮兄弟"},{"target":"char_xing_rong","type":"挚友","intensity":65,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"同僚"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[272],"source_refs":[{"chapter":272,"line_start":3,"line_end":3,"text":"寇仲领着桂锡良和幸容"}]},{"id":"char_xing_rong","name":"幸容","alias":["幸副堂主"],"identity":"竹花帮副堂主","faction":"竹花帮","role":"companion","archetype":"warrior","rank":"略有小成","one_line":"竹花帮副堂主，寇仲的帮中兄弟","personality":{"traits":["忠义","勇敢","务实","沉着","服从"],"speech_style":"简洁","temperament":"沉着"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_kou_zhong","type":"合作者","intensity":60,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"竹花帮兄弟"},{"target":"char_gui_xi_liang","type":"挚友","intensity":65,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"同僚"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[272],"source_refs":[{"chapter":272,"line_start":3,"line_end":3,"text":"寇仲领着桂锡良和幸容"}]},{"id":"char_shen_bei_chang","name":"沈北昌","alias":[],"identity":"竹花帮香主级头领","faction":"竹花帮","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"竹花帮香主级头领，沉稳持重","personality":{"traits":["沉稳","冷静","务实","果断","老练"],"speech_style":"沉稳","temperament":"冷静"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_kou_zhong","type":"合作者","intensity":60,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"竹花帮同僚"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[272],"source_refs":[{"chapter":272,"line_start":5,"line_end":7,"text":"沈北昌、骆奉和玉玲夫人迎上来"}]},{"id":"char_luo_feng","name":"骆奉","alias":[],"identity":"竹花帮香主级头领","faction":"竹花帮","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"竹花帮香主级头领，与沈北昌同级","personality":{"traits":["忠诚","务实","谨慎","团结","老练"],"speech_style":"稳重","temperament":"稳重"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_kou_zhong","type":"合作者","intensity":60,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"竹花帮同僚"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[272],"source_refs":[{"chapter":272,"line_start":5,"line_end":7,"text":"沈北昌、骆奉和玉玲夫人迎上来"}]},{"id":"char_yu_ling_fu_ren","name":"玉玲夫人","alias":[],"identity":"竹花帮有影响力的女性头领","faction":"竹花帮","role":"npc","archetype":"scholar","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"竹花帮中极具影响力的女性，性格刚烈","personality":{"traits":["刚烈","正义","有影响力","果敢","直率"],"speech_style":"娇哼","temperament":"刚烈"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_kou_zhong","type":"合作者","intensity":60,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"竹花帮同僚"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[272],"source_refs":[{"chapter":272,"line_start":5,"line_end":12,"text":"沈北昌、骆奉和玉玲夫人迎上来"}]},{"id":"char_shao_ling_zhou","name":"邵令周","alias":[],"identity":"竹花帮内奸，借外力对付帮中兄弟","faction":"竹花帮","role":"villain","archetype":"scholar","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"竹花帮叛徒，勾结外人对付帮中兄弟","personality":{"traits":["奸诈","背信","阴险","自利","卑劣"],"speech_style":"阴险","temperament":"阴险"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_kou_zhong","type":"对手","intensity":70,"bond_level":2,"dynamic":"帮内对手"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[272],"source_refs":[{"chapter":272,"line_start":11,"line_end":12,"text":"邵令周这么借外人之力来对付帮中兄弟"}]},{"id":"char_li_zi_tong","name":"李子通","alias":[],"identity":"江都军阀，寇仲的对手","faction":"江都军","role":"villain","archetype":"warrior","rank":"出神入化","one_line":"江都军阀，与寇仲敌对","personality":{"traits":["阴险","自利","狡猾","胆怯","反复"],"speech_style":"阴险","temperament":"阴险"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_kou_zhong","type":"宿敌","intensity":80,"bond_level":1,"dynamic":"敌对"},{"target":"char_du_fu_wei","type":"对手","intensity":75,"bond_level":1,"dynamic":"军阀争霸"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[272],"source_refs":[{"chapter":272,"line_start":3,"line_end":3,"text":"由李子通、左孝友等亲自送出总管府"}]},{"id":"char_zuo_xiao_you","name":"左孝友","alias":[],"identity":"李子通麾下将领","faction":"江都军","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"李子通麾下将领","personality":{"traits":["忠诚","勇猛","服从","沉稳","务实"],"speech_style":"简洁","temperament":"沉稳"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_li_zi_tong","type":"主仆","intensity":70,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"部属"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[272],"source_refs":[{"chapter":272,"line_start":3,"line_end":3,"text":"由李子通、左孝友等亲自送出总管府"}]}],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[{"id":"faction_zhu_hua_bang","name":"竹花帮","type":"帮派","location":"江都","sub_divisions":["堂口"],"one_line":"江都地区的重要帮派，内部出现分裂","source_refs":[{"chapter":272,"line_start":9,"line_end":9,"text":"十多名竹花帮香主级的头领在等候"}]}],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":2,"line_start":33,"line_end":78,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_shi_fei_xuan","speaker_name":"师妃暄","listener":"char_xu_zi_ling","text":"听子陵兄的口气，似是对妃暄有所不满。","tone":"疑问","chapter":272,"line_start":33,"line_end":34},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":"char_shi_fei_xuan","text":"师小姐不着世尘，自是来去自如，不受任何牵制。不过我徐子陵却是一个凡人，心中尚有问题相询，但看来小姐是不会答我的！","tone":"苦笑","chapter":272,"line_start":37,"line_end":40},{"speaker":"char_shi_fei_xuan","speaker_name":"师妃暄","listener":"char_xu_zi_ling","text":"这误会真大。刚才妃暄问子陵兄你往何处去，你却避而不答。妃暄非但平凡，更是个爱以牙还牙的女子，只好有所保留，你还敢来怪人家。","tone":"调侃","chapter":272,"line_start":43,"line_end":46},{"speaker":"char_shi_fei_xuan","speaker_name":"师妃暄","listener":"char_xu_zi_ling","text":"怎么忽然会变成哑巴的？你现在只能是入川去，究竟是甚么天大重要的事，可令你抛下你的少帅兄弟，千里迢迢赶往巴蜀？","tone":"调侃","chapter":272,"line_start":51,"line_end":54},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":"char_shi_fei_xuan","text":"师小姐若要知道，补问一句不就成吗？为何却绕个弯子来耍我？","tone":"苦笑","chapter":272,"line_start":57,"line_end":59},{"speaker":"char_shi_fei_xuan","speaker_name":"师妃暄","listener":"char_xu_zi_ling","text":"因为妃暄直到这一刻，仍摸不清楚你是怎样的一个人，所以才以各种旁敲侧击来试探。","tone":"陈述","chapter":272,"line_start":61,"line_end":62},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":"char_shi_fei_xuan","text":"我是这么难了解的吗？","tone":"疑问","chapter":272,"line_start":65,"line_end":65},{"speaker":"char_shi_fei_xuan","speaker_name":"师妃暄","listener":"char_xu_zi_ling","text":"妃暄自问擅于观人之道。但到现仍弄不清楚你和寇仲两个。寇仲因有所追求，所以比较易于窥测，但你却像一个难识深浅的水井，表面看来简单，但总摸不到你的底子；所以才生出好奇心，想知道你究竟从何人处得悉这么多有关魔门两派六道的秘密。今趟入川，又有何贵干。","tone":"认真","chapter":272,"line_start":67,"line_end":71},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":"char_shi_fei_xuan","text":"事实上我并不打算隐瞒任何事。因为我今次入川找的是石青璇，且事情该和师小姐有莫大的关系。","tone":"坦然","chapter":272,"line_start":73,"line_end":75},{"speaker":"char_shi_fei_xuan","speaker_name":"师妃暄","listener":"char_xu_zi_ling","text":"究竟是甚么事？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":272,"line_start":77,"line_end":77}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_shi_fei_xuan","name":"师妃暄","alias":["师小姐"],"identity":"慈航静斋传人，仙态岸然的美女","faction":"慈航静斋","role":"companion","archetype":"scholar","rank":"登峰造极","one_line":"慈航静斋传人，智慧过人，武功高强的出尘女子","personality":{"traits":["智慧","出尘","善辩","观察力强","温柔","有主见"],"speech_style":"温婉含蓄","temperament":"悠然自若"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_xu_zi_ling","type":"合作者","intensity":70,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"互相试探的同伴"},{"target":"char_kou_zhong","type":"合作者","intensity":60,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"合作对付魔门"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[272],"source_refs":[{"chapter":272,"line_start":33,"line_end":34,"text":"师妃暄别转娇躯，面向徐子陵"}]},{"id":"char_xu_zi_ling","name":"徐子陵","alias":["子陵兄"],"identity":"寇仲挚友，身怀绝技的青年高手","faction":"无","role":"protagonist","archetype":"warrior","rank":"出神入化","one_line":"寇仲挚友，淡然洒脱的绝顶高手","personality":{"traits":["洒脱","坦然","机智","深沉","重义","淡泊"],"speech_style":"洒脱自然","temperament":"洒脱"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_kou_zhong","type":"挚友","intensity":95,"bond_level":5,"dynamic":"生死与共的兄弟"},{"target":"char_shi_fei_xuan","type":"合作者","intensity":65,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"互相试探的同伴"},{"target":"char_shi_qing_xuan","type":"恋人","intensity":75,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"寻找中的心上人"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[272],"source_refs":[{"chapter":272,"line_start":37,"line_end":40,"text":"徐子陵洒然笑道"}]}],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[{"id":"faction_ci_hang_jing_zhai","name":"慈航静斋","type":"武林门派","location":"巴蜀","sub_divisions":[],"one_line":"正道圣地，以师妃暄为代表的武林正派","source_refs":[{"chapter":272,"line_start":33,"line_end":34,"text":"师妃暄别转娇躯"}]}],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":3,"line_start":79,"line_end":132,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":null,"text":"李子通肯这么低声下气，眼白白的放我这大仇人走，可见他心知肚明再无力抵抗老杜这新一轮的攻城战。所以我们是许胜不许败，若让老杜夺得江都，我们都要卷铺盖找地方滚，江淮军可不是说笑的。","tone":"认真","chapter":272,"line_start":83,"line_end":86},{"speaker":"char_luo_qi_fei","speaker_name":"洛其飞","listener":"char_kou_zhong","text":"这正是少帅在此见到其飞的原因。我曾三次易容混入清流，终查到杜伏威手下有一名叫陈盛的年青将军，此人勇猛擅战，极得杜伏威倚重，假若我们能乔装沈军伏杀此人，杜伏威悲愤下会不顾一切去进攻沈纶。","tone":"陈述","chapter":272,"line_start":89,"line_end":91},{"speaker":"char_bu_tian_zhi","speaker_name":"卜天志","listener":"char_kou_zhong","text":"据其飞观察所得，陈盛那支五千人的部队，该在明晚离开六合，以支援向江都开来的陆上先头部队。","tone":"陈述","chapter":272,"line_start":93,"line_end":95},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":"char_luo_qi_fei","text":"六合是什么地方？","tone":"疑问","chapter":272,"line_start":97,"line_end":97},{"speaker":"char_luo_qi_fei","speaker_name":"洛其飞","listener":"char_kou_zhong","text":"六合是清流东滁水旁的另一县城，贯通长江水路，从那里顺风顺流只一天可抵江都。陈盛管的正是泊在六合的江淮水师，大小船只达七十多艘。","tone":"陈述","chapter":272,"line_start":99,"line_end":102},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":null,"text":"这么短的水程，偷袭将是难比登天。","tone":"惊讶","chapter":272,"line_start":105,"line_end":105},{"speaker":"char_chen_chang_lin","speaker_name":"陈长林","listener":"char_kou_zhong","text":"事实上亦不容我们偷袭。由六合至江都，全在杜伏威的严密控制下，我们只能以迅雷不及掩耳的手法，一举命中陈盛的帅船，再登船把他杀死。因此人精擅水战，故对沈法兴威胁甚大，更可令杜伏威深信不疑是沈纶的部下所为。","tone":"认真","chapter":272,"line_start":107,"line_end":110},{"speaker":"char_luo_qi_fei","speaker_name":"洛其飞","listener":"char_kou_zhong","text":"沈纶的人中有个使枪的高手，人称'长枪郎'古俊，身形雄伟，与少帅有点近似，若少帅不用刃而用枪，刺杀陈盛，沈纶即管跳下长江，都洗不清嫌疑。","tone":"陈述","chapter":272,"line_start":113,"line_end":115},{"speaker":"char_bu_tian_zhi","speaker_name":"卜天志","listener":"char_kou_zhong","text":"我特别调来七艘最适合在附近水域作这种狙击用途的快船，更把它们改装成可冒充海沙帮的战船。到时将以海沙帮惯用的战法，进行突袭，包保没有人能瞧出破绽。","tone":"得意","chapter":272,"line_start":117,"line_end":120},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":null,"text":"各位叔伯兄弟，有甚么指示，即管吩咐小弟去做吧！","tone":"豪迈","chapter":272,"line_start":123,"line_end":124},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":null,"text":"若我能够分身的话，云玉真休想可活着溜返巴陵。","tone":"愤怒","chapter":272,"line_start":129,"line_end":130}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_luo_qi_fei","name":"洛其飞","alias":[],"identity":"寇仲麾下情报人员","faction":"寇仲军","role":"companion","archetype":"scholar","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"寇仲麾下情报人员，擅长易容潜入","personality":{"traits":["机智","谨慎","忠诚","观察力强","沉着"],"speech_style":"稳重","temperament":"沉着"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_kou_zhong","type":"主仆","intensity":75,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"部属"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[272],"source_refs":[{"chapter":272,"line_start":89,"line_end":91,"text":"洛其飞道"}]},{"id":"char_bu_tian_zhi","name":"卜天志","alias":[],"identity":"寇仲麾下水军将领","faction":"寇仲军","role":"companion","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"寇仲麾下水军将领，负责战船调配","personality":{"traits":["勇猛","兴奋","忠诚","务实","自信"],"speech_style":"豪爽","temperament":"兴奋"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_kou_zhong","type":"主仆","intensity":75,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"部属"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[272],"source_refs":[{"chapter":272,"line_start":93,"line_end":95,"text":"卜天志接口道"}]},{"id":"char_chen_chang_lin","name":"陈长林","alias":[],"identity":"寇仲麾下将领，精通水战","faction":"寇仲军","role":"companion","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"寇仲麾下将领，精通水战，负责摇橹","personality":{"traits":["精通水战","忠诚","沉稳","务实","老练"],"speech_style":"稳重","temperament":"沉稳"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_kou_zhong","type":"主仆","intensity":75,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"部属"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[272],"source_refs":[{"chapter":272,"line_start":81,"line_end":81,"text":"撑艇的是陈长林"}]},{"id":"char_chen_sheng","name":"陈盛","alias":[],"identity":"杜伏威麾下年青将军，精擅水战","faction":"杜伏威军","role":"villain","archetype":"warrior","rank":"出神入化","one_line":"杜伏威麾下年青将军，勇猛擅战，精擅水战","personality":{"traits":["勇猛","擅战","年轻有为","精擅水战","得势"],"speech_style":"威严","temperament":"勇猛"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_du_fu_wei","type":"主仆","intensity":80,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"部属"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[272],"source_refs":[{"chapter":272,"line_start":89,"line_end":91,"text":"杜伏威手下有一名叫陈盛的年青将军"}]},{"id":"char_du_fu_wei","name":"杜伏威","alias":["老杜"],"identity":"江淮军统帅，寇仲的大敌","faction":"杜伏威军","role":"villain","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登峰造极","one_line":"江淮军统帅，寇仲的大敌，实力雄厚","personality":{"traits":["雄才大略","冷酷","果断","猜忌","强势"],"speech_style":"威严","temperament":"强势"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_kou_zhong","type":"宿敌","intensity":85,"bond_level":1,"dynamic":"大敌"},{"target":"char_li_zi_tong","type":"对手","intensity":75,"bond_level":1,"dynamic":"军阀争霸"},{"target":"char_chen_sheng","type":"主仆","intensity":80,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"倚重部属"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[272],"source_refs":[{"chapter":272,"line_start":83,"line_end":86,"text":"杜伏威"}]},{"id":"char_yun_yu_zhen","name":"云玉真","alias":[],"identity":"巴陵方面人物，与寇仲有仇","faction":"巴陵","role":"villain","archetype":"assassin","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"巴陵方面人物，与寇仲有仇怨","personality":{"traits":["狡猾","背叛","自私","阴险","善逃"],"speech_style":"狡猾","temperament":"狡猾"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_kou_zhong","type":"对手","intensity":70,"bond_level":2,"dynamic":"仇敌"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[272],"source_refs":[{"chapter":272,"line_start":129,"line_end":130,"text":"云玉真休想可活着溜返巴陵"}]},{"id":"char_shen_fa_xing","name":"沈法兴","alias":[],"identity":"沈纶之父，江都附近军阀","faction":"沈法兴军","role":"villain","archetype":"warrior","rank":"出神入化","one_line":"江都附近军阀，沈纶之父","personality":{"traits":["雄心","狡诈","强势","军事才能","野心勃勃"],"speech_style":"威严","temperament":"强势"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_du_fu_wei","type":"对手","intensity":75,"bond_level":1,"dynamic":"军阀争霸"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[272],"source_refs":[{"chapter":272,"line_start":107,"line_end":110,"text":"沈法兴"}]},{"id":"char_shen_lun","name":"沈纶","alias":[],"identity":"沈法兴之子，被嫁祸的对象","faction":"沈法兴军","role":"villain","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"沈法兴之子，被嫁祸刺杀陈盛","personality":{"traits":["年轻","冲动","有野心","军事才能","被利用"],"speech_style":"冲动","temperament":"冲动"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_shen_fa_xing","type":"亲属","intensity":80,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"父子"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[272],"source_refs":[{"chapter":272,"line_start":113,"line_end":115,"text":"沈纶"}]},{"id":"char_gu_jun","name":"古俊","alias":["长枪郎"],"identity":"沈纶麾下使枪高手","faction":"沈法兴军","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"出神入化","one_line":"沈纶麾下使枪高手，人称长枪郎","personality":{"traits":["勇猛","使枪高手","身形雄伟","强悍","威猛"],"speech_style":"威猛","temperament":"勇猛"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_shen_lun","type":"主仆","intensity":70,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"部属"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[272],"source_refs":[{"chapter":272,"line_start":113,"line_end":115,"text":"人称'长枪郎'古俊"}]}],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[{"id":"faction_du_fu_wei_jun","name":"杜伏威军","type":"帮派","location":"江淮","sub_divisions":[],"one_line":"江淮军，杜伏威统领的军事力量","source_refs":[{"chapter":272,"line_start":83,"line_end":86,"text":"江淮军"}]},{"id":"faction_shen_fa_xing_jun","name":"沈法兴军","type":"帮派","location":"江都附近","sub_divisions":[],"one_line":"沈法兴统领的军事力量","source_refs":[{"chapter":272,"line_start":107,"line_end":110,"text":"沈法兴"}]},{"id":"faction_hai_sha_bang","name":"海沙帮","type":"帮派","location":"长江水域","sub_divisions":[],"one_line":"长江水域的帮派，被寇仲军冒充","source_refs":[{"chapter":272,"line_start":117,"line_end":120,"text":"海沙帮"}]}],"locations":[{"id":"loc_liu_he","name":"六合","region":"清流","one_line":"清流东滁水旁的县城，江淮水师泊地","source_refs":[{"chapter":272,"line_start":99,"line_end":102,"text":"六合是清流东滁水旁的另一县城"}]},{"id":"loc_qing_liu","name":"清流","region":"江淮","one_line":"江淮地区城池","source_refs":[{"chapter":272,"line_start":89,"line_end":91,"text":"清流"}]},{"id":"loc_jiang_du","name":"江都","region":"江淮","one_line":"江淮重镇，各方势力争夺的焦点","source_refs":[{"chapter":272,"line_start":83,"line_end":86,"text":"江都"}]}],"items":[{"id":"item_meng_chong_dou_jian","name":"蒙冲斗舰","type":"weapon","owner":"char_kou_zhong","one_line":"海沙帮惯用的改装战船，用于伪装突袭","description":"小型战船，船身不大但轻便灵活，左右船舷建有女墙可护半身，女墙下有棹孔供桨探出，划桨水兵全部掩藏船内，船身蒙生牛皮用以防火，是海沙帮惯用的战法工具。","effects":["轻便灵活","防火","隐蔽性强"],"origin":"海沙帮","rarity":"上乘佳品","related_characters":["char_kou_zhong"],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[272],"source_refs":[{"chapter":272,"line_start":293,"line_end":294,"text":"被称为蒙冲斗舰"}]}]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":4,"line_start":133,"line_end":253,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_shi_fei_xuan","speaker_name":"师妃暄","listener":"char_xu_zi_ling","text":"杨虚彦竟是石之轩的徒弟！","tone":"惊讶","chapter":272,"line_start":133,"line_end":133},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":"char_shi_fei_xuan","text":"他不但是石之轩的徒弟，更是旧隋废太子杨勇的儿子。因为石之轩的另一身份就是着作《西域图记》的裴矩，师小姐对此可有甚么联想？","tone":"认真","chapter":272,"line_start":135,"line_end":138},{"speaker":"char_shi_fei_xuan","speaker_name":"师妃暄","listener":"char_xu_zi_ling","text":"多谢子陵兄，这一番话解开不少石之轩的悬疑。不知这些关系重大的消息，是得自何方？","tone":"认真","chapter":272,"line_start":141,"line_end":143},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":"char_shi_fei_xuan","text":"照我和寇仲猜想，石青璇该不知谁是花间派这一代的传人，故杨虚彦会打算凭某种方法，骗取石青璇的信任，以得到石之轩交予女儿保管的典籍。","tone":"陈述","chapter":272,"line_start":145,"line_end":147},{"speaker":"char_shi_fei_xuan","speaker_name":"师妃暄","listener":"char_xu_zi_ling","text":"石青璇并非花间派典籍的托管人。假若我猜得不错，杨虚彦该是看上藏在幽林小筑的《不死印卷》。这印卷落在任何人手上都绝无用途，只有杨虚彦和侯希白这两个石之轩传人，才有天大的好处。","tone":"认真","chapter":272,"line_start":149,"line_end":152},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":"char_shi_fei_xuan","text":"石之轩与'不死印卷'究竟又是甚么一回事呢？","tone":"疑问","chapter":272,"line_start":155,"line_end":156},{"speaker":"char_shi_fei_xuan","speaker_name":"师妃暄","listener":"char_xu_zi_ling","text":"无论对我们又或魔门来说，石之轩都是近百年来最令人头痛的祸害，观乎此人能只手单拳，兵不血刃的覆亡大隋，弄得天下四分五裂，便可想见他的厉害。若非秀心师伯使他动了真情，令他融合正邪各家之长而创的不死印奇功出现绝不该有的破绽，天下可能将不是现在这番情境。","tone":"苦涩","chapter":272,"line_start":159,"line_end":162},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":"char_shi_fei_xuan","text":"不死印究竟是如何可怕的一种邪功，是否练成就可以死不去。它比之天魔大法和道心种魔又如何？","tone":"疑问","chapter":272,"line_start":165,"line_end":167},{"speaker":"char_shi_fei_xuan","speaker_name":"师妃暄","listener":"char_xu_zi_ling","text":"这世上那有能令人长生不死的功法。长保这臭皮囊更非明智之举，子陵兄有否听过佛家四宗？","tone":"平静","chapter":272,"line_start":169,"line_end":172},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":"char_shi_fei_xuan","text":"听曹应龙提过，好像是天台、三论、华严和禅宗，石之轩还曾偷学过三论宗嘉祥大师和禅宗四祖的秘技。","tone":"陈述","chapter":272,"line_start":175,"line_end":177},{"speaker":"char_shi_fei_xuan","speaker_name":"师妃暄","listener":"char_xu_zi_ling","text":"看来曹应龙确有悔过之心，所说更非胡诌，因为这都是四宗从没有向外人透露的秘密。石之轩乃武学的绝世奇才，无论甚么奇功秘笈，到了他手内，总能融汇贯通，且又另出枢机，更上层楼。在武林史上，恐怕只有你和寇仲才有资格与之相提并论。","tone":"认真","chapter":272,"line_start":179,"line_end":185},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":"char_shi_fei_xuan","text":"师小姐谬奖哩！","tone":"谦虚","chapter":272,"line_start":187,"line_end":188},{"speaker":"char_shi_fei_xuan","speaker_name":"师妃暄","listener":"char_xu_zi_ling","text":"不用客气。你和寇仲都是在当今武林中令人直到此刻仍难以相信的奇迹。不死印如何厉害，先不去说，只看佛家四大高僧当年曾联手追杀石之轩，务要收回他的武功，三次围击，仍给他负伤逃去，当可知石之轩的可怕。","tone":"认真","chapter":272,"line_start":191,"line_end":194},{"speaker":"char_shi_fei_xuan","speaker_name":"师妃暄","listener":"char_xu_zi_ling","text":"子陵兄倘以为四高僧武功平常，就大错特错。他们所以名不显于江湖，只因他们真是方外之人，从不卷入江湖俗事内，故不像宁道奇般名震天下。当年嘉祥和四祖联同天台宗的智慧大师、华严宗的帝心尊者，追捕石之轩，连阴癸派都噤若寒蝉，不敢插手或沾惹，便知四大圣僧的厉害。论实力，四圣僧任何一人都足与宁道奇难分轩轾。","tone":"严肃","chapter":272,"line_start":197,"line_end":203},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":"char_shi_fei_xuan","text":"那岂非石之轩比之祝玉妍和向雨田更厉害？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":272,"line_start":205,"line_end":206},{"speaker":"char_shi_fei_xuan","speaker_name":"师妃暄","listener":"char_xu_zi_ling","text":"又不可以这么比较，只可说他们是同级数的人物。至于谁高谁低，除非他们真正一决雌雄，否则难知结果。","tone":"平静","chapter":272,"line_start":209,"line_end":212},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":"char_shi_fei_xuan","text":"刚才小姐说过对魔门来说，石之轩也是个大祸害，又是甚么意思？","tone":"疑问","chapter":272,"line_start":215,"line_end":216},{"speaker":"char_shi_fei_xuan","speaker_name":"师妃暄","listener":"char_xu_zi_ling","text":"因为石之轩有心一统魔道，所以对魔门各派的领袖，有一定的威胁。祝玉妍便对之极为忌惮。如非被秀心师伯破去他的不死印，祝玉妍恐怕早保不住她魔门第一人的至尊地位。","tone":"陈述","chapter":272,"line_start":219,"line_end":222},{"speaker":"char_shi_fei_xuan","speaker_name":"师妃暄","listener":"char_xu_zi_ling","text":"现在石之轩不死印奇功的唯一破绽就是酷肖秀心师伯的女儿，亦是唯一能令石之轩不能忘情的人。曹应龙对石之轩确有很深的了解，假若石青璇有甚么不测，石之轩或可回复邪王本色，再没有任何牵挂。所以我们无论用甚么手段，都要阻止杨虚彦奸计得逞，否则已够纷乱的天下，会出现更不可知的变数。","tone":"严肃","chapter":272,"line_start":229,"line_end":234},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":"char_shi_fei_xuan","text":"师小姐是否准备和在下一起赶往幽林小谷呢？","tone":"疑问","chapter":272,"line_start":237,"line_end":238},{"speaker":"char_shi_fei_xuan","speaker_name":"师妃暄","listener":"char_xu_zi_ling","text":"妃暄惯于一人独来独往，子陵兄只要入住成都少城南市的悦来栈，妃暄自会寻你。","tone":"歉然","chapter":272,"line_start":241,"line_end":242},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":"char_shi_fei_xuan","text":"看情况吧！","tone":"淡然","chapter":272,"line_start":245,"line_end":245}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_yang_xu_yan","name":"杨虚彦","alias":["影子刺客"],"identity":"石之轩徒弟，旧隋废太子杨勇之子","faction":"魔门花间派","role":"villain","archetype":"assassin","rank":"出神入化","one_line":"石之轩徒弟，影子刺客，旧隋废太子杨勇之子","personality":{"traits":["阴险","野心勃勃","武功高强","狡诈","隐忍"],"speech_style":"阴险","temperament":"阴险"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_shi_zhi_xuan","type":"师徒","intensity":80,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"师徒"},{"target":"char_shi_qing_xuan","type":"对手","intensity":75,"bond_level":2,"dynamic":"觊觎其典籍"},{"target":"char_hou_xi_bai","type":"对手","intensity":70,"bond_level":2,"dynamic":"同门竞争"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[272],"source_refs":[{"chapter":272,"line_start":133,"line_end":138,"text":"杨虚彦竟是石之轩的徒弟"}]},{"id":"char_shi_zhi_xuan","name":"石之轩","alias":["裴矩","邪王"],"identity":"魔门邪王，花间派传人，近百年来最令人头痛的祸害","faction":"魔门花间派","role":"villain","archetype":"scholar","rank":"返璞归真","one_line":"魔门邪王，武学绝世奇才，覆亡大隋的幕后推手","personality":{"traits":["武学奇才","深不可测","亦正亦邪","心机深沉","用情至深","可怕"],"speech_style":"深沉","temperament":"深不可测"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_yang_xu_yan","type":"师徒","intensity":80,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"师徒"},{"target":"char_hou_xi_bai","type":"师徒","intensity":75,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"师徒"},{"target":"char_shi_qing_xuan","type":"亲属","intensity":85,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"父女"},{"target":"char_xiu_xin","type":"恋人","intensity":