{"segment":5,"line_start":254,"line_end":311,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":null,"text":"我们的战船在那里？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":272,"line_start":257,"line_end":257},{"speaker":"char_bu_tian_zhi","speaker_name":"卜天志","listener":"char_kou_zhong","text":"要瞒过江淮军的探子，自然要有点手段。我们利用绞盘和长木条造成的滑架，把七艘战船拖到岸上，再以树木掩盖，保证不露任何破绽。","tone":"得意","chapter":272,"line_start":259,"line_end":262},{"speaker":"char_chen_chang_lin","speaker_name":"陈长林","listener":"char_kou_zhong","text":"这是海沙帮最擅长运用的小型战船，利于冲锋破敌。有风张帆，无风划桨。左右船舷各建女墙，可护半身，不惧强弓硬矢。女墙下有棹孔，供桨探出，而划桨水兵全部掩藏船内。","tone":"陈述","chapter":272,"line_start":275,"line_end":280},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":"char_chen_chang_lin","text":"这些洞口是否用来放箭的，开大些是否会好些儿呢？","tone":"疑问","chapter":272,"line_start":283,"line_end":285},{"speaker":"char_chen_lao_mou","speaker_name":"陈老谋","listener":"char_kou_zhong","text":"这些叫弩窗，又或牙孔，专供发射强弩之用，所以不用太大，也可瞄准发射。","tone":"陈述","chapter":272,"line_start":287,"line_end":288},{"speaker":"char_bu_tian_zhi","speaker_name":"卜天志","listener":"char_chen_lao_mou","text":"还差甚么功夫？","tone":"疑问","chapter":272,"line_start":291,"line_end":291},{"speaker":"char_chen_lao_mou","speaker_name":"陈老谋","listener":"char_bu_tian_zhi","text":"只差尚未给船身蒙上生牛皮，用以防火，这是海沙帮惯用的手法，被称为蒙冲斗舰，今次的假装陷害可说落足工夫。","tone":"得意","chapter":272,"line_start":293,"line_end":294},{"speaker":"char_luo_qi_fei","speaker_name":"洛其飞","listener":"char_kou_zhong","text":"这趟行动确曾经过反覆推敲，熟虑深思，我们不敢把战船开来，就是怕令江淮军生出疑心。这七艘船均是由别处绕大弯分别驶来的，如此才更能令杜伏威深信不疑。","tone":"认真","chapter":272,"line_start":297,"line_end":300},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":null,"text":"若我是老爹，亦要中计。哈！现在我唯一该做的事，是否好好睡一觉呢？","tone":"得意","chapter":272,"line_start":303,"line_end":304},{"speaker":"char_chen_lao_mou","speaker_name":"陈老谋","listener":"char_kou_zhong","text":"少帅放心睡吧！最好是到船上睡，到时到候老夫会把你唤醒。再为你易容改扮，否则怎来一章'长枪郎古俊大江勇诛陈盛'呢？","tone":"大笑","chapter":272,"line_start":307,"line_end":310}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_chen_lao_mou","name":"陈老谋","alias":[],"identity":"寇仲麾下工匠，负责战船改装","faction":"寇仲军","role":"npc","archetype":"scholar","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"寇仲麾下工匠，负责战船改装和易容","personality":{"traits":["工匠","自信","老练","幽默","专业"],"speech_style":"豪爽","temperament":"自信"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_kou_zhong","type":"主仆","intensity":70,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"部属"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[272],"source_refs":[{"chapter":272,"line_start":267,"line_end":310,"text":"陈老谋正指挥手下"}]}],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
